Angelines Fernández https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angelines_Fern%C3%A1ndez 0 María de los Ángeles "Angelines" Fernández Abad (July 9, 1922 – March 25, 1994) was a Spanish-born Mexican actress of film and television. She is best remembered for playing Doña Clotilde "La Bruja del 71" in the sitcom El Chavo del Ocho.
